sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Пользователь
    participant Browser as Browser (JS Fetch)
    participant REST as MissionRestController (Inbound Adapter)
    participant UC as AppEngine (Application Core)
    participant Store as MissionStore (Domain Core)
    participant Repo as MissionRepository (Outbound Port)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Database)

    Note over User, DB: Сценарий: Поиск миссий через Web-интерфейс
    
    User->>Browser: Вводит текст в строку поиска
    Browser->>REST: GET /api/missions?search="..."
    activate REST
    
    REST->>UC: getStore().find(specification)
    activate UC
    
    UC->>Store: find(FullTextSpecification)
    activate Store
    
    Store->>Repo: findAll()
    activate Repo
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM missions
    activate DB
    DB-->>Repo: ResultSet / Data
    deactivate DB
    Repo-->>Store: List<Mission>
    deactivate Repo
    
    Store->>Store: Business Logic: Stream Filter (Specification)
    
    Store-->>UC: filteredList
    deactivate Store
    
    UC-->>REST: filteredList
    deactivate UC
    
    REST->>REST: Jackson Serialization (Object -> JSON)
    REST-->>Browser: 200 OK (JSON Array)
    deactivate REST
    
    Browser->>Browser: Update DOM (table)
    Browser-->>User: Обновление списка миссий на странице
